                        "content": "\n<div class=\"space-y-12 font-sans text-slate-200\">\n    <div class=\"text-center py-12\">\n        <div class=\"inline-block p-4 rounded-full bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 mb-6 text-5xl\">\ud83d\udcc9</div>\n        <h2 class=\"text-4xl md:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-6\">\n            5.1 __slots__: Memory Optimization\n        </h2>\n    </div>\n    <p>Prevent creation of <code>__dict__</code> to save RAM on millions of objects.</p>\n<div class=\"bg-[#0f1014] p-6 rounded-3xl border border-slate-800 relative overflow-hidden my-8\">\n    <div class=\"absolute top-0 right-0 p-2 bg-slate-800 rounded-bl-xl text-[10px] font-mono text-slate-400\">main.py</div>\n    <pre class=\"font-mono text-sm text-slate-300 overflow-x-auto\"><code class=\"language-python\">\nclass Point:\n    __slots__ = ['x', 'y']\n    def __init__(self, x, y):\n        self.x = x\n        self.y = y\n        # self.z = 10 -> AttributeError\n</code></pre>\n</div>\n\n</div>\n"
